      in the ImageSetConfiguration.yaml file by running the oc-mirror command. For
      example: ```terminal $ oc mirror - v2 c <mirror_config_directory>/ImageSetConfiguration.yaml
      file://<mirror_archive_directory>/ ``` where: <mirror_config_directory>:: Enter
      the location of your image set configuration file on your system, for example,
      .user. <mirror_archive_directory>:: Enter the location of your directory where
      the mirror archive will be created, for example, file://.user. [NOTE] ---- Running
      the oc-mirror command generates a local workspace containing the mirror archive
      file, the Helm chart, ImageDigestMirrorSet (IDMS) and ImageTagMirrorSet (ITMS)
