      You can load a custom Developer Hub theme from a dynamic plugin. 1. Export a
      theme provider function in your dynamic plugin, for example: Sample myTheme.ts
      fragment ```javascript import { lightTheme } from ''./lightTheme''; // some
      custom theme import { UnifiedThemeProvider } from ''@backstage/theme''; export
      const lightThemeProvider = ({ children }: { children: ReactNode }) => ( <UnifiedThemeProvider
