      creating a custom theme, see Backstage documentation - Creating a Custom Theme.
      2. Configure Developer Hub to load the theme in the UI by using the themes configuration
      field: app-config.yaml fragment ```yaml dynamicPlugins: frontend: example.my
      custom theme plugin: themes: id: light title: Light variant: light icon: someIconReference
