      a persistent volume claim (PVC) to ensure that the cache persists when you restart
      the RHDH application. For more information about using the dynamic plugins cache,
      see Using the dynamic plugins cache. You have created a persistent volume claim
      (PVC) for the dynamic plugins cache with the name dynamic plugins root. You
