      namespace and verify the secret: ```bash $ oc -n openshift-logging create secret
      generic splunk-secret --from-literal=hecToken=<HEC_Token> ``` ```bash $ oc -n
      openshift-logging get secret/splunk-secret -o yaml ``` 6. Create a basic `ClusterLogForwarder`resource
