      catalog-info.yaml file. These annotations merge with and take precedence over
      the global rules. The annotation key must use the format ''scorecard.io/{providerId}.thresholds.rules.{thresholdKey}:
      ''{expression}''''. This system follows a specific order of precedence where
      higher-priority configurations, such as entity-specific annotations, override
      lower-priority settings like the global defaults.'
