      logged in as an administrator on the OpenShift Container Platform web console.
      You also need to have configured the appropriate roles and permissions within
      your project to create or access an application, and you must have installed
      Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform 4.16 to 4.20. Finally, you must make sure
      that your system meets the minimum sizing requirements.
