    - 'Deploying Red Hat Developer Hub on OpenShift Container Platform with the Operator
      As a developer, you can deploy a Red Hat Developer Hub instance on OpenShift
      Container Platform by using the Developer Catalog in the Red Hat OpenShift Container
      Platform web console. This deployment method uses the Red Hat Developer Hub
      Operator. You have set the baseUrl in your app config.yaml to match the external
