      cannot communicate, and features might not work as expected. An OpenShift Container
      Platform administrator has installed the Red Hat Developer Hub Operator. You
      have provisioned your custom config maps and secrets in your <my rhdh project>
      project. You have authored your Backstage custom resource. 1. In the OpenShift
      Container Platform web console, select your <{my_product_namespace}> project,
      then click Add. 2. From the Developer Catalog panel, click Operator Backed.
