      Secondly, because the RBAC plugin is disabled by default, you must author a
      custom `dynamic-plugins.yaml` file. In this file, you need to enable the plugin
      by including the entry for `package: ./dynamic plugins/dist/backstage community
      plugin rbac` and setting its `disabled` status to `false`.'
